                    <img src="img/landing-2.png" class="img-fluid mx-auto mb-3 shadow-sm rounded-4" 
                         alt="Landing 2" style="max-height: 220px; object-fit: contain;">
                    <h4 class="fw-bold text-success mb-2">Best Quality Products For Your Family</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted small">Aliquam imperdiet mauris lacus, a elementum ex imperdiet sit amet donec vulputate.</p>
                </div>
